<view class="page-container">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="config-header">
      <text class="section-title">超时阈值配置</text>
      <button class="btn-primary save-btn" loading="{{saving}}" disabled="{{saving || loading}}" bindtap="onSave">保存</button>
    </view>

    <view class="config-tip">
      <text>预警天数须小于对应超时天数；总体超时天数须不小于设计超时与施工超时之和。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="field-group" wx:for="{{fieldGroups}}" wx:key="index">
      <view class="form-item half-item" wx:for="{{item}}" wx:for-item="field" wx:key="key">
        <text class="form-label">{{field.label}}</text>
        <view class="number-row">
          <input
            class="form-input number-input"
            type="digit"
            value="{{field.value}}"
            data-field="{{field.key}}"
            bindinput="onNumberInput"
          />
          <text class="unit-label">天</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="config-header">
      <text class="section-title">自动督办发送策略</text>
      <button class="btn-primary save-btn" loading="{{savingAutoReminder}}" disabled="{{savingAutoReminder || loading}}" bindtap="onSaveAutoReminder">保存</button>
    </view>

    <view class="config-tip">
      <text>固定按北京时间执行。普通批次用于预警和常规超时；紧急批次仅用于超时事件或特急工单。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="field-group">
      <view class="form-item half-item">
        <text class="form-label">发送开始时间</text>
        <input
          class="form-input"
          value="{{autoReminderForm.businessWindowStart}}"
          data-field="businessWindowStart"
          placeholder="08:30"
          bindinput="onAutoInput"
        />
      </view>
      <view class="form-item half-item">
        <text class="form-label">发送结束时间</text>
        <input
          class="form-input"
          value="{{autoReminderForm.businessWindowEnd}}"
          data-field="businessWindowEnd"
          placeholder="18:30"
          bindinput="onAutoInput"
        />
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="field-group">
      <view class="form-item half-item">
        <text class="form-label">检查间隔</text>
        <view class="number-row">
          <input
            class="form-input number-input"
            type="number"
            value="{{autoReminderForm.checkIntervalMinutes}}"
            data-field="checkIntervalMinutes"
            bindinput="onAutoNumberInput"
          />
          <text class="unit-label">分钟</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="form-item half-item">
        <text class="form-label">批次宽限</text>
        <view class="number-row">
          <input
            class="form-input number-input"
            type="number"
            value="{{autoReminderForm.batchGraceMinutes}}"
            data-field="batchGraceMinutes"
            bindinput="onAutoNumberInput"
          />
          <text class="unit-label">分钟</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item full-item">
      <text class="form-label">普通发送批次</text>
      <input
        class="form-input"
        value="{{normalBatchText}}"
        data-type="normal"
        placeholder="09:00、14:30、17:30"
        bindinput="onBatchTextInput"
      />
      <text class="helper-text">用顿号、逗号或空格分隔，格式 HH:mm。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item full-item">
      <text class="form-label">紧急发送批次</text>
      <input
        class="form-input"
        value="{{urgentBatchText}}"
        data-type="urgent"
        placeholder="18:20"
        bindinput="onBatchTextInput"
      />
      <text class="helper-text">仅超时事件或特急工单使用，可留空。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="field-group">
      <view class="form-item half-item">
        <text class="form-label">单工单日上限</text>
        <view class="number-row">
          <input
            class="form-input number-input"
            type="number"
            value="{{autoReminderForm.maxSendsPerDemandPerDay}}"
            data-field="maxSendsPerDemandPerDay"
            bindinput="onAutoNumberInput"
          />
          <text class="unit-label">次</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="form-item half-item">
        <text class="form-label">单事件日上限</text>
        <view class="number-row">
          <input
            class="form-input number-input"
            type="number"
            value="{{autoReminderForm.maxSendsPerEventPerDay}}"
            data-field="maxSendsPerEventPerDay"
            bindinput="onAutoNumberInput"
          />
          <text class="unit-label">次</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="load-more" wx:if="{{loading}}"><text>加载中...</text></view>
</view>
